<p><strong>Terrain:</strong> the city is predominantly flat, with the River Ljubljanica running through the centre and the castle on top of a small hill</p>
<p><strong>Best time to go:</strong> end of May to mid-October</p>
<p><strong>Recommended for:</strong> easy city walks, families, activities, sightseeing, food and drink</p>
<p><strong>Fly into:</strong> Ljubljana or Salzburg</p>
<p><strong>Fly from: </strong>London Gatwick, London Heathrow, Birmingham, Manchester, Newcastle and Glasgow</p>
<p><strong>Transfer time:</strong> Approx. 1 hour from Ljubljana airport or 3-4 hours (traffic dependent, including a stop) from Salzburg airport</p>
